{"tid":1128724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】33台灣人抵港擬參與遊行 遭入境處強制遣返","createTime":"2019-04-28T04:27:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-28T04:52:25.000Z","uid":28366,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"07b3a145a1a4c8b29672a74253affd0dfe42e492","tid":1128724,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T04:27:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/6pcRlpM9FXYrV_8LjY6vXw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTc2OA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/nuEFWP3UX8Ixnw4ILhbgkA--~B/aD00MDA7dz01MDA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20190427a221959.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F6pcRlpM9FXYrV_8LjY6vXw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTc2OA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FnuEFWP3UX8Ixnw4ILhbgkA--~B%2FaD00MDA7dz01MDA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20190427a221959.jpg&h=64c0e2e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】民陣明日發行反對《逃犯條例》修訂遊行，有33名台灣宗教團體人士昨日飛抵香港，計劃參加遊行，卻遭入境處拒絕入境並強制遣返。處方回覆傳媒查詢時指，在處理每宗入境個案時，均會依據法律和既定入境政策，考慮個別個案的情況後，作出批准或拒絕入境的決定。<br />\n<br />\n據台媒報道，陸委會今日表示，已向港府表達關切，並要求港府應尊重並理性看待台灣人合法表達意見；又指香港辦事處當時並未接獲台灣人相關協助請求，但知悉事件後，已即洽航空公司了解情況，並對事件表示遺憾；強調台港交流向來緊密，希望港府能善待持合法證件入境的台灣人。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，過往已有台灣人被拒入境香港的事件，例如去年台獨樂團「閃靈樂團」獲邀來港演出、2017年台灣學者吳叡人及吳介民教授申請赴港簽證被拒、台灣傳媒人張鐵志亦被拒入境等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/逃犯條例-33台灣人抵港擬參與遊行-遭入境處強制遣返-141700050.html?fbclid=IwAR12yMvGjsT4CI9Aln1iL7aBxm5GCmXRzTIL4M-Im6iaA7J9kERdPQpOpvA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-33%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E4%BA%BA%E6%8A%B5%E6%B8%AF%E6%93%AC%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E9%81%AD%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83%E8%99%95%E5%BC%B7%E5%88%B6%E9%81%A3%E8%BF%94-141700050.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR12yMvGjsT4CI9Aln1iL7aBxm5GCmXRzTIL4M-Im6iaA7J9kERdPQpOpvA&d=VPc2G2a59adbLf1ajQMU8lQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=e1b2fa89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/逃犯條例-33台灣人抵港擬參與遊行-遭入境處強制遣返-141700050.html?fbclid=IwAR12yMvGjsT4CI9Aln1iL7aBxm5GCmXRzTIL4M-Im6iaA7J9kERdPQpOpvA</a>"},{"pid":"c38010c3f6f19b4a6570e53e8398ff6d8da9afe6","tid":1128724,"uid":250905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T04:34:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24ac17b6ff02b7d6573915f57b0d8584fb85fb53","tid":1128724,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T04:35:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">焦土派又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"b03b3126a42a95edc3a7be5955b60eb6bed01681","tid":1128724,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T04:44:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f9fcefd7a081ebf2fcd8dffbc281b3f9fa1effb","tid":1128724,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T04:52:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}